<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - 页面未找到</title>
    <style>
        /* 基础重置与字体 */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fc; /* 柔和的背景色 */
            color: #333;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* 主容器 */
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        /* 404 大号数字 */
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: -20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
        }

        /* 插画容器 */
        .error-illustration {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .error-illustration svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1));
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        /* 文本内容 */
        .error-message h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #2d3748;
        }

        .error-message p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #718096;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* 按钮组 */
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 主按钮 */
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #4f46e5; /* 品牌主色 */
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #4338ca;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 8px -1px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
        }

        /* 次要按钮 */
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: white;
            color: #4a5568;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            border-color: #cbd5e0;
            color: #2d3748;
        }

        /* 动画定义 */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }

        /* 移动端适配 */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .error-code {
                font-size: 5rem;
                letter-spacing: -2px;
            }
            
            .error-illustration {
                width: 150px;
                height: 150px;
            }

            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="error-container">
        <!-- 背景大数字 -->
        <div class="error-code">404</div>

        <!-- 插画 (使用内联SVG) -->
        <div class="error-illustration">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <!-- 简单的迷路宇航员/星球插画风格 -->
                <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" fill="#e0e7ff" />
                <path d="M60 130 Q 100 180 140 130" fill="none" stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <circle cx="100" cy="80" r="30" fill="#4f46e5" />
                <circle cx="100" cy="80" r="35" fill="none" stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.5"/>
                <path d="M85 70 Q 100 60 115 70" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"/>
                <circle cx="90" cy="75" r="2" fill="white"/>
                <circle cx="110" cy="75" r="2" fill="white"/>
                <!-- 装饰星星 -->
                <path d="M160 40 L165 50 L175 50 L167 58 L170 70 L160 62 L150 70 L153 58 L145 50 L155 50 Z" fill="#fbbf24" />
                <circle cx="40" cy="160" r="5" fill="#cbd5e0" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- 文字信息 -->
        <div class="error-message">
            <h2>哎呀，页面走丢了</h2>
            <p>抱歉，我们找不到您请求的页面。<br>它可能已被删除、重命名或暂时不可用。</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 按钮操作 -->
        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">返回首页</a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-secondary">返回上一页</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>